Let say, I'm going to do this
rice storage business.

00:34:41.220 --> 00:34:41.930
I can do it.

00:34:41.930 --> 00:34:44.310
It's open to anybody
in the world.

00:34:44.310 --> 00:34:45.580
I can find a warehouse.

