the price of any futures

00:41:14.320 --> 00:41:18.580
contract, p sub f, is the
futures price on one of those

00:41:18.580 --> 00:41:27.380
dates, is equal to 1 plus r,
plus s, times the spot price.

00:41:29.960 --> 00:41:32.420
Where the spot price,
p sub s --

