00:42:15.140 --> 00:42:17.920
So, if it's one year and
the interest rate is

00:42:17.920 --> 00:42:20.580
5%, then r is 0.05.

00:42:20.580 --> 00:42:24.100
But if it's one and a half
years, it's going to be more

00:42:24.100 --> 00:42:27.980
