So, the normal situation in
futures markets is contango,

00:42:59.660 --> 00:43:04.150
which means that prices are
normally going up through

00:43:04.150 --> 00:43:10.070
time, because the longer in the
future we're looking at,

00:43:10.070 --> 00:43:14.550
the longer time that we're
losing interest and storage.

