00:45:24.290 --> 00:45:25.640
No uncertainty.

00:45:25.640 --> 00:45:28.170
What do futures prices do?

00:45:28.170 --> 00:45:31.290
Well, let's consider a futures
market that's --

00:45:31.290 --> 00:45:34.580
