expiration date goes down.

00:46:16.120 --> 00:46:19.005
And so, this r goes down,
and s goes down.

00:46:19.005 --> 00:46:22.010
And eventually, it hits 0
on the expiration date.

00:46:22.010 --> 00:46:24.700
And the futures price equals
the spot price on the

00:46:24.700 --> 00:46:26.700
expiration date.

00:46:26.700 --> 00:46:30.395
But in reality, we don't see
such a nice and perfect match.

