00:51:54.290 --> 00:51:58.040
And they care about, what
kind of oil do I get?

00:51:58.040 --> 00:51:59.430
And when is it going
to be delivered?

00:51:59.430 --> 00:52:01.050
And what are you going to
do for me, if it's not

00:52:01.050 --> 00:52:03.100
delivered on time?

00:52:03.100 --> 00:52:05.580
They have complicated
delivery contracts.

00:52:05.580 --> 00:52:07.950
Almost all oil is sold
